  "name": "Distracting Chatter",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You bombard a target with distracting auditory illusions, surrounding them with a tumultuous cacophony of overlapping speech, whispers, screams, and muttering. The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Off-Guard}, takes a -2 status penalty to purely auditory Perception checks, and must succeed at a @Check[type:flat|dc:5] to use auditory abilities or verbal spell components. Similarly, a creature who attempts to affect the target with an auditory effect must succeed at a @Check[type:flat|dc:5] or the attempt fails. The duration depends on the target's Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The duration is 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The duration is 3 rounds.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The duration is 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (7th)</strong> You can target up to five creatures.</p>"
    },
